---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
description: AI tools reviews, tutorials and guides by Geo Vega — Intel Analyst turned AI Generalist.
---
<style>
  .hero { padding: 3rem 0 2rem; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #f3ece0; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .hero h1 span { color: #22d3ee; }
  .hero p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #888; max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .cta { display: inline-block; background: #22d3ee; color: #0f0f0f; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.65rem 1.4rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .cta:hover { text-decoration: none; opacity: 0.9; }
  .recent { margin-top: 3.5rem; }
  .recent h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .post-list { list-style: none; }
  .post-list li { border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a; padding: 0.9rem 0; }
  .post-list a { font-weight: 600; color: #e8e2d9; }
  .post-list a:hover { color: #22d3ee; text-decoration: none; }
  .post-date { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #555; margin-top: 0.15rem; }
</style>
<div class="hero">
  <h1>AI tools, reviewed by <span>someone who uses them</span></h1>
  <p>Intel Analyst turned AI Generalist. I test and document AI tools as I build with them — Agent OS, Hermes, OpenClaw, and more.</p>
  <a href="/blog/" class="cta">Read the blog →</a>
</div>
<div class="recent">
  <h2>Recent posts</h2>
  <ul class="post-list">
  {% for post in collections.posts | limit(5) %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      <div class="post-date">{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</div>
    </li>
  {% else %}
    <li style="color:#555;font-style:italic">First post coming soon.</li>
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>
